overview: British comedy award-winner, BAFTA nominee and self-styled Morissey impersonator Harry Hill performs live at London's prestigious Palace Theatre during his sell-out Birdstrike! Tour. Featuring: TV show band "The Caterers" Stouffer the Cat History of Popular Music Gymnastic Display The Good Friday Agreement Fun Spot Human-human-interface-Quiz-ball and,of course SILD
title: Harry Hill - Birdstrike!
